member.name: P:prjAssignment.My.Resources.Resources.ReturningABike
member.summary: Looks up a localized string similar to To Return a City Bike Push the City Bike back into an available stand. An audio beep is emitted and the lights on the bike stand flash momentarily before a continuous green light is displayed. This confirms that the bike has been replaced correctly and the hire has been terminated. If there is a problem, either try to reposition the bike or try another stand..
